text = "Tips and Tricks:
- Once a task is created in the To-do list, it can be moved
   between the \"To Do,\" \"Doing,\" and \"Done\" columns 
   using the arrows or deleted using the trashcan icon

- The Schedule Builder requires each event to have a set 
  time (between 6AM and 11PM) and individual events 
  can be deleted using the trashcan icon

- The Habit Tracker contains sliders to track the daily
  completion of several pre-built habits

- All data is reset on a daily basis"

